These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, board-games, writing
House: tower, modern, farmhouse, art-deco
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, polish, egyptian, turkish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, march, august
 1. the modern house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the art-deco house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
10. the egyptian is on the right of the polish##1
11. the polish is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Hobby    | board-games   | skydiving       | video-games | writing   |
| House        | modern    | art-deco  | farmhouse      | tower |
| Nationality         | turkish      | polish | egyptian         | brazilian   |
| Birthday   | april | november       | march        | august   |

