House: victorian, cape-cod, colonial, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing, filmmaking, chess
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, balloon-flower, marigold, amaryllis
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the victorian house##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is the person who likes purple##1
4. the person who likes lilac is between the cape-cod house and the person who growsaconite##2
5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3
9. the cape-cod house is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Color           | blood-red | lilac | red | purple |
| House   | victorian  | colonial | cape-cod         | futuristic      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking      | rock-climbing    | chess         | sudoku   |
| Flower     | aconite         | balloon-flower    | amaryllis          | marigold         |

