.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, scooter, skateboard, trike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, martial-arts, horror, scientific
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, dahlia, daffodil, begonia
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, architect, freelancer, analyst
 1. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the architect##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the architect is on the left or right of the analyst##3
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the designer##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is between the freelancer and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 9. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Transport          | scooter | trike  | bike | skateboard      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster       | scientific    | martial-arts      | horror      |
| Flower           | begonia     | poppy     | dahlia         | daffodil   |
| Job         | freelancer | designer | architect     | analyst |

