5. the person who's sport is rugby is the colonial house##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
8. the person eating cucumber is between the person who likes turquise and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
9. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3

.:: Answer ::.
