 6. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
 8. the pilot is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is between the musician and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
