4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman, pall-mall, vegafina
 1. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 5. the chaman-smoker is between the person eating avocado and the dannemann-smoker##2
