 7. the person who growssunflower is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person who growsdahlia##2
 8. the person drinking sprite is the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Food         | avocado | grapes     | orange  | cucumber |
