4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, turtle, fish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, chef, mechanic, dancer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, may, april
 1. the dancer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the frog##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the mechanic##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is the dancer##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the chef##3
11. the person drinking tea is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Pet         | cat      | fish | turtle       | frog   |
| Beverage   | tea     | iced-tea | mirinda | fanta |
| Job   | freelancer    | chef     | mechanic        | dancer       |
| Birthday     | may | november   | january   | april       |

