.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku, drawing, board-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, subway, airplane
City: colone, prague, nizza, rome
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, ivory, brown, purple
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes ivory##2
 5. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 6. the person traveling to colone is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who likes pink##2
 7. the person traveling to nizza is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person traveling to colone is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby          | sudoku | board-games   | drawing   | puzzles |
| Transport           | jet-ski   | subway     | skateboard   | airplane |
| City   | prague    | colone    | rome   | nizza   |
| Color         | pink    | ivory | purple | brown    |

 